BLUE SHIFT

a. Controls

W - Up
S - Down
A - Left
D - Right
Shift - Time Shift
Esc - Pause

b. What is it about?

A time-shifter returns to a fallen civilisation in ruins. 
Using her time-shifting ability, she attempts to make her way to the CORE, crossing various obstacles and defeating her enemies. 
What could she possibly hope to achieve?

The environment in the present sometimes differ from that of the past. 
Use TIME SHIFT by pressing [SHIFT] key to shift between the Past and the Present.

c. Group name and members

